{"tid":2096552,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘇惠德拒電單車手足保釋","createTime":"2020-07-06T07:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:26:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":195,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"705e2348871d0f91a85b20e4e6e6af0e992cd246","tid":2096552,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/27222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F27222&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=485334f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/27222</a><br />\n<br />\n據了解，首名被控港區国安法之人士被拒絕保釋，將押後至10月上旬再訊。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官引用港區国安法第42條拒絕保釋。條文指除非法庭相信被告不會再危害中国安全，否則不能給予保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告被控煽動分裂中国及恐怖活動兩罪，前者最高監禁10年，後者最高刑罰為終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞"},{"pid":"40497151cae2ed395ad713daf472bb2e3446b70a","tid":2096552,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080d56d99dc8be287942feb24f68985609d3be1d","tid":2096552,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"10月6日再訊"},{"pid":"b50bd64ed326ee0a9c7886ae22a111908e1b3618","tid":2096552,"uid":68111,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老母 未審就先坐"},{"pid":"40a398303dadfb7cb483f6a85b03a35f0c186149","tid":2096552,"uid":188176,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"咁就鎖三個月<br />\n都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dd0e72e8c34785fe1cf643c775446c4c30db17","tid":2096552,"uid":124630,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾官知批保有後果，唔批冇後果，基本上所有同類案都冇咩機會批<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b096eac5392f9428399a19620c1c879fb7daab","tid":2096552,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"080d56d99dc8be287942feb24f68985609d3be1d","tid":2096552,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"10月6日再訊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3ea53b6998d0a9e73e71544d87c686982921f3","tid":2096552,"uid":33709,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"根本你放邊個官都一樣<br />\n條法例講明唔可以保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a343df621ba1809215ff5ee94e04e895ea18116","tid":2096552,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F6662&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=f8aeedbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6662</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第三庭 <br />\n#蘇惠德總裁判官 #指定法官<br />\n#港區國安法<br />\n#20200701灣仔<br />\n<br />\n唐(23)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 煽動他人分裂國家罪 (違反《港區國安法》第20條及第21條)<br />\n<br />\n於7月1日在灣仔菲林明道、軒尼詩道、駱克道、盧押道、謝斐道煽動他人組織、策劃、實施或者參與實施旨在分裂國家、破壞國家統一行為，不論是否使用武力或者以武力相威脅，即將香港特別行政區從中華人民共和國分離出去或非法改變香港特別行政區的法律地位<br />\n<br />\n(2) 恐怖活動罪 (違反《港區國安法》第24條)<br />\n<br />\n於7月1日在灣仔菲林明道、軒尼詩道、駱克道、盧押道、謝斐道為脅迫中央人民政府或香港特別行政區政府或者威嚇公眾以圖實現政治主張，實施造成或者意圖造成嚴重社會危害的恐怖活動，即針對人的嚴重暴力或以其他危險方法危害公眾安全。控方透露被告高速駕駛電單車，曾三次衝向警方防線，至少3名警員身體受到嚴重傷害<br />\n<br />\n被告人坐輪椅，左手包紮，精神充足<br />\n<br />\n裁判官拒絕准予被控人保釋<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至10月6日1430時於西九龍裁判法院第三庭再訊"},{"pid":"682e843c4d47d777cf2d7a2dd929d9ea12b95bb6","tid":2096552,"uid":194298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"點撚樣危害中国安全呀?"},{"pid":"f6e0ae85e8427dab51b0d62320dfcc3926848259","tid":2096552,"uid":68111,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"10dd0e72e8c34785fe1cf643c775446c4c30db17","tid":2096552,"uid":124630,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾官知批保有後果，唔批冇後果，基本上所有同類案都冇咩機會批<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"已經痴撚曬線 保釋既原意俾國安法一句 就改變左<br />\n到底普通法仲存唔存在"},{"pid":"b9986ff9ac3b868c29d58a5c5de2181ef0a194dd","tid":2096552,"uid":158546,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"一日未審都唔會有進展<br />\n咁法庭永遠都唔會覺得佢有改變架啦<br />\n即係未審都一定冇得保釋直到審果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後罪成坐到死為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1013f1f5ceb29ce74c36af7ff0dce10d9a547b8","tid":2096552,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"682e843c4d47d777cf2d7a2dd929d9ea12b95bb6","tid":2096552,"uid":194298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"點撚樣危害中国安全呀?"},"citedBy":1,"